1.We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.					
2. We have considered Provisional Data till 30-11-2019 for the purpose of this certificate.The Firm has deposited 100% amount received from allottees in RERA Account as against 70% requirement. The Payment of Statotory Taxes includes payment by way of Cash and payment by utilisation of credit.The Promoter has not opened separate Acount as per RERA Regulation Guidelines.In case of Land we have considered book as Land cost till date.

The Guidance Note requires that we comply with the ethical requirements of the Code of Ethics issued by the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India.					
5. The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project  solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.
